		<title>A century of discovery: Mayo Clinic Proceedings marks 100 years of advancing medical research, education and practice</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/a-century-of-discovery-mayo-clinic-proceedings-marks-100-years-of-advancing-medical-research-education-and-practice/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jay Furst]]></dc:creator>
