		<title>Mayo Clinic team takes quantum leap to win global competition&nbsp;with brain-signal model</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-team-takes-quantum-leap-to-win-global-competition-with-brain-signal-model/</link>
		
